<paragraph id="8BE6D86CFFA7FF979C91C2208D11F812" blockId="116.[151,1437,479,2026]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis id="B92D047EFFA7FF979C91C22088A8F889" bold="true" box="[198,451,1879,1905]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">
<typeStatus id="54E266CEFFA7FF979C91C2208846F889" box="[198,301,1879,1905]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">Neotype</typeStatus>
designation
</emphasis>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC8A59DFFA7FF979D85C22F8B01F88A" author="Bezzi, M." box="[466,618,1880,1906]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117" pagination="442 - 496" refId="ref102728" refString="Bezzi, M. (1912) Rhagionidae et Empididae ex insula Formosa a clar. H. Sauter missae. Annales Historico-Naturales Musei Nationalis Hungarici, 10, 442 - 496." type="journal article" year="1912">Bezzi (1912)</bibRefCitation>
described this species from a few specimens taken by H. Sauter from Takao and 
<collectingRegion id="499D168EFFA7FF979D4CC2F78801F862" box="[283,362,1920,1946]" country="Taiwan" name="Tainan" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">Tainan</collectingRegion>
and later (1914) he noted that this species is quite common on the island. The type of 
<taxonomicName id="4C59A3EFFFA7FF9799D4C2F7886CF839" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Elaphropeza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="116" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melanura">
<emphasis id="B92D047EFFA7FF9799D4C2F7886CF839" italics="true" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">E. melanura</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was deposited in the Hungarian Museum (Budapest) and it was destroyed in 1956 (Papp and Földvári, pers. comm.). The specimens housed in the 
<collectionCode id="ED4840A9FFA7FF979E82C2A78A6DF812" box="[725,774,2000,2026]" country="Germany" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:33211" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:33211" name="Senckenberg Deutsches Entomologisches Institut" pageId="116" pageNumber="117" type="Other type of research institution/biorepository">DEI</collectionCode>
are not 
<typeStatus id="54E266CEFFA7FF979F32C2A78AA0F812" box="[869,971,2000,2026]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117">syntypes</typeStatus>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFC8A59DFFA7FF979F8CC2A78D06F812" author="Bezzi, M." box="[987,1133,2000,2026]" pageId="116" pageNumber="117" pagination="65 - 78" refId="ref102761" refString="Bezzi, M. (1914) H. Sauter's Formosa-Ausbeute. Rhagionidae et Empididae. Supplementa Entomologica, Berlin, 3, 65 - 78." type="journal article" year="1914">Bezzi, 1914</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
